nodes.text: Na'Lora was an individual who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.

Na'Lora was the manager of a Tarasin band. During the celebrations for Cularin's 200th anniversary in 31 BBY, Na'Lora was present in Vanster Enan's Sop House in Gadrin on the planet Cularin, where the band was playing.
